text:
It's so cold~...!
It feels like it's piercing through even with a jacket on...!

Yeah...
I wonder if everyone is okay...?

Hmm...
I wish there was some warm drink or something.

It seems like they're getting it ready~
But we'll have to wait a bit longer~

So... How about we have oshikura manju
together? It'll warm us up!

I vote for it~!
It's definitely better to keep moving~!

Oshikura manju~ Don't cry as you're being pushed~!
Ahahaha...!
